      "writtenOn": "2019-11-08T15:21:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Technically the URL should be a the type definition above, not at usage. Semantically you want to define what it is when you declare something, not when it\u0027s being used. Here I agree it\u0027s borderline because it\u0027s \"one use\" but I still think I\u0027d prefer to move (or copy) the URL above.",
